Ruth Lee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruth_Lee 0 Ruth Lee (September 14, 1895 - August 3, 1975) was an American actress. Lee was born in Minneapolis, Minnesota. Lee acted in stock theater with the National Theatre in Washington, D.C.Lee died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles, California. She was married to the actor Grandon Rhodes.
